### 3. 目标选择系统

战斗中如何从多个候选目标中选择攻击对象？目标选择系统回答这个问题。

#### 常见选择策略

| 策略 | 描述 | 适用场景 |
|------|------|---------|
| **最近优先** | 选择距攻击者最近的目标 | 防御塔、近战单位 |
| **最弱优先** | 选择生命值最低的目标 | 输出型角色、集火策略 |
| **最强优先** | 选择生命值最高的目标 | 坦克仇恨拉住 |
| **随机选择** | 随机选择目标 | 辅助敌人、AI 随机性 |
| **权重系统** | 根据多因素加权计算优先级 | 复杂 AI 决策 |

#### 优先级权重系统

实际游戏中，通常需要综合考虑多个因素：

```typescript
// TargetSelection.ts
interface TargetingParams {
  distanceWeight: number;    // 距离权重
  healthWeight: number;      // 生命值权重（低血量高优先级）
  threatWeight: number;      // 仇恨值权重
}

selectTarget(
  candidates: Entity[],
  params: TargetingParams
): Entity | null {
  if (candidates.length === 0) return null;

  let bestTarget: Entity | null = null;
  let highestScore = -Infinity;

  for (const candidate of candidates) {
    const score = this.calculateScore(candidate, params);
    if (score > highestScore) {
      highestScore = score;
      bestTarget = candidate;
    }
  }

  return bestTarget;
}

private calculateScore(
  target: Entity,
  params: TargetingParams
): number {
  const distScore = 1 / (1 + this.owner.getPosition().distance(target.getPosition()));
  const healthScore = 1 - (target.getHealth() / target.getMaxHealth()); // 血量越低分数越高
  const threatScore = target.getThreatLevel();

  return (
    distScore * params.distanceWeight +
    healthScore * params.healthWeight +
    threatScore * params.threatWeight
  );
}
```

> [!example]- 目标选择实现
> ```typescript
> // 不同策略的实现
> enum TargetStrategy {
>   NEAREST,
>   WEAKEST,
>   STRONGEST,
>   RANDOM,
>   WEIGHTED,
> }
>
> class TargetSelector {
>   select(
>     candidates: Entity[],
>     strategy: TargetStrategy,
>     params?: TargetingParams
>   ): Entity | null {
>     if (candidates.length === 0) return null;
>
>     switch (strategy) {
>       case TargetStrategy.NEAREST:
>         return this.selectNearest(candidates);
>       case TargetStrategy.WEAKEST:
>         return this.selectWeakest(candidates);
>       case TargetStrategy.STRONGEST:
>         return this.selectStrongest(candidates);
>       case TargetStrategy.RANDOM:
>         return candidates[Math.floor(Math.random() * candidates.length)];
>       case TargetStrategy.WEIGHTED:
