### 8. 战斗反馈设计（打击感）

打击感是动作游戏的核心，决定了战斗的"爽感"。

#### 五大反馈要素

| 要素 | 效果 | 实现难度 |
|------|------|---------|
| **屏幕震动** | 传递冲击力 | 容易 |
| **命中停顿** | 强化打击感 | 中等 |
| **粒子特效** | 视觉反馈 | 中等 |
| **音效配合** | 听觉反馈 | 中等 |
| **数值飘字** | 信息反馈 | 容易 |

#### 屏幕震动（Screen Shake）

```typescript
// ScreenShake.ts
export class ScreenShake {
  private camera: Camera;
  private originalPos: Vec3;
  private intensity: number = 0;
  private duration: number = 0;

  shake(intensity: number, duration: number) {
    this.intensity = intensity;
    this.duration = duration;
    this.originalPos = this.camera.node.position.clone();
  }

  update(dt: number) {
    if (this.duration <= 0) return;

    this.duration -= dt;
    const shake = this.originalPos.add(new Vec3(
      (Math.random() - 0.5) * this.intensity,
      (Math.random() - 0.5) * this.intensity,
      0
    ));
    this.camera.node.position = shake;

    this.intensity *= 0.9; // 衰减
  }
}
```

#### 命中停顿（Hit Stop）

命中时短暂冻结游戏，让玩家感受"拳拳到肉"：

```typescript
// HitStop.ts
export class HitStopManager {
  private timeScale: number = 1;
  private freezeDuration: number = 0;

  triggerHitStop(duration: number) {
    this.freezeDuration = duration;
    this.timeScale = 0; // 冻结
  }

  update(dt: number) {
    if (this.freezeDuration > 0) {
      this.freezeDuration -= dt;
      if (this.freezeDuration <= 0) {
        this.timeScale = 1;
      }
    }
  }

  getTimeScale(): number {
    return this.timeScale;
  }
}
```

使用时：
```typescript
// 攻击命中时
hitStopManager.triggerHitStop(0.05); // 50ms 停顿
screenShake.shake(0.3, 0.15);        // 屏幕震动
playHitEffect(hitPoint);              // 特效
playHitSound();                       // 音效
showDamagePopup(damage);             // 飘字
```

